      <title>韩国法院开始审查尹永哲弹劾案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/south-korea-s-ruling-party-leader-resigns-after-yoon-impeachment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国宪法法院已开始审查总统尹锡烈的弹劾案，据报道，调查人员计划本周就其令人震惊的戒严宣言对其进行讯问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/south-korea-s-ruling-party-leader-resigns-after-yoon-impeachment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 02:17:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平辩称清洗是“不可避免的”党内斗争的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/xi-says-inevitable-for-ruling-party-to-have-internal-conflicts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据中国国家主席习近平今年 1 月在一次反腐败会议上发表的最新讲话，他表示，执政党共产党内部的分裂不可避免，同时呼吁加大力度建立纪律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/xi-says-inevitable-for-ruling-party-to-have-internal-conflicts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 01:52:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>弹劾案解除时间短暂，韩元和股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/korean-won-stocks-take-spotlight-after-impeachment-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈遭弹劾后出现的反弹在周一被证明是短暂的，随着人们的注意力迅速从政治转移到经济，股市和货币逆转了早盘的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/korean-won-stocks-take-spotlight-after-impeachment-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
